name: UNCEASING VIXEN 20:37
description: She likes the lights off for the mystery. Never to hide in the shadows, but to emanate from them. Her exhale from the darkness illuminates with an unceasing shimmer. A vixen vastly potent with the sweet smell of femininity. The gentleness of a forgone love was somehow lost in translation, yet speaking a naked truth. Her gospel is not for the weak or foolish. Nothing sappy, just pristine ravishment with a gentle smitten feeling. She persuades you to be better and compensates you for following through. She is a vixen lusted after by the Olympians with more allure than a goddess of the Pantheon.
